'''Birendra Agrahari''' (also spells as Virendra) is a [[People of Nepal|Nepalese]] playback singer who primarily sings in [[Nepali language|Nepali]], [[Oriya language|Oriya]], [[Hindi]] and [[Bhojpuri]] languages. He lent his voice for a debut Nepali film [[Pareni Maya Jalaima|Undone By Love]] starring [[Dilip Rayamajhi]] and [[Jharana Bajracharya]] in 2004 which was released in Hong Kong and [[Nepal]].<ref>{{cite web|title= Birendra Agrahari's Filmography |url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1762363/filmotype|work=|publisher=|accessdate=15 February 2013}}</ref>
