== Career == Birendra made his film debut with a song for the movie [[Pareni Maya Jalaima]] (Undone By Love) in 2004. He sings for several Nepali films, albums and has performed in many stage shows and events. Birendra sang in the music album ''Rumal Chhod Jau''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Hiun Bhanda by Suman Chhetri and Birendra Agrahari |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O2epNKOv4Cg|work=|publisher=Youtube.com|accessdate=15 February 2013}}</ref>
