'''Lounes Laouzai''' (born 26 December 1989 in [[Tizi Ouzou]]) is an [[Algeria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who is currently playing for [[MC Saïda]] in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1]].
==Career== Laouzai signed with [[MC Alger]] from [[JS Bordj Ménaïel]] in the summer of 2007. In 2009, he joined [[MFK Topvar Topoľčany]] in the [[Slovak Second League]].<ref>[http://www.dzfoot.com/joueur.php?joueur_id=1513&saison_id=13 La Fiche de Lounes LAOUZAI - Football algérien<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080305071552/http://www.dzfoot.com/joueur.php?joueur_id=1513&saison_id=13 |date=2008-03-05 }}</ref> In 2010, he returned to [[Algeria]] and signed with [[MC Saïda]].
